# Exact — environment variables
#
# The calculus engine (solver.py + index.html) runs ENTIRELY in the browser and
# needs no secrets. Today the only server-side secret is for the photo-OCR
# serverless function (api/read.js), which reads a problem image with Claude vision.
#
# Heads-up: Exact is moving to bring-your-own-key — the API key will live in the
# visitor's own browser, not on the server — after which this file needs no secrets.
#
# Copy to `.env` for local work; set the real value in your host's env. Never commit it.

ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=your-anthropic-key-here
